lated field This is the ninth successful year of the SMaRT Program and thus far     students have successfully completed this summer research internship training program      SMART PROGRAM APPLICATION      SMART PROGRAM APPLICATION Key dates         Deadline extended from March    due to technical issues  Mail signed and completed SMaRT Program Application along with three     signed letters of reference       Selected students will begin their internship with orientation and training       Students will present their experience through interviews  oral presentations  and scientific posters Please complete the application  print  sign and return by mail to  Janet Stull Snow College of Medicine Rockford Department of Biomedical Sciences      Parkview Avenue Rockford If you have questions regarding the program uic edu jlss uic edu About Education Research Patient Care Departments News Giving INFORMATION FOR  Prospective and Current Students Faculty   Staff Alumni   Friends Patients Businesses and Community RESOURCES  UIC Directory Blackboard Emergency Information Contact Us Apply Now Give Contact Us If you have questions  comments  or problems accessing this site  please E mail the webmaster College of Medicine Chicago Peoria Rockford Urbana 